Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.54,0:00:17.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（目覚ましの音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.45,0:00:22.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子(れつこ)）痛っ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:22.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:26.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うう…\Nマジ 頭 痛い 痛(いて)てて…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.79,0:00:26.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,My head really hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.50,0:00:28.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,しばらく お酒控えよう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.66,0:00:28.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No more alcohol for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.95,0:00:32.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.66,0:00:38.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何 このハンカチ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.75,0:00:38.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Whose handkerchief is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.50,0:00:40.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（かぐ音）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.33,0:00:41.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私のじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.45,0:00:41.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.29,0:00:45.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,昨日\N何があったんだっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.45,0:00:45.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.16,0:00:51.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:51.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:54.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？ えっ？ えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:00:59.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何？ 今の
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.37,0:01:01.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何？ 今の
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:04.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.45,0:01:03.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RAGE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.91,0:01:41.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.87,0:01:49.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（フェネ子(こ)）こないだ\Nどうやって帰ったか覚えてる？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:49.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember\Nhow you got back home?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:51.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,気付いたら 家で寝てた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.95,0:01:51.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.87,0:01:53.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何にも覚えてない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.04,0:01:53.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.29,0:01:56.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,自腹王子に\N介抱してもらったことも？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.41,0:01:56.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Not even the Prince taking care of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.08,0:02:03.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,覚えてない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.20,0:02:03.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Retsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.70,0:02:07.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（坪根(つぼね)）ちょっと 烈子さん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ はい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:12.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Please deliver this to Shimada\Nin the Sales department.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.54,0:02:12.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,これ 営業部の島田(しまだ)さんに\N届けてきてちょうだい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:14.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はい 分かりました
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:14.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.25,0:02:17.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それと れさすけ君て分かる？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.37,0:02:17.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know Resasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,彼に “出すものは 早めに出せ”\Nって くぎ刺しといて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.20,0:02:21.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell him to make his submissions ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.70,0:02:24.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,不在なら メモでいいから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:23.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,If he's not there, leave him a note.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.00,0:02:35.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田(だ)）おう 烈子\N（烈子）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.16,0:02:34.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Retsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ ハイ田君 おはよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Haida. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.20,0:02:39.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:43.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when do you drink canned coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:43.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お前 缶コーヒーなんて\N飲むやつだったっけ？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:47.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ これ？ アハハ…\N何となく飲んでみたくなっちゃって
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.54,0:02:47.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this? I thought I'd give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.33,0:02:49.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）フーン
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.70,0:02:52.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ ごめん
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.87,0:02:56.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Miss Tsubone asked me to hurry,\Nso I'll see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.33,0:02:56.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,坪根さんに せかされてるから\N行くね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.79,0:02:58.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ハイ田）あっ ああ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.91,0:02:58.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.50,0:03:05.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,SALES DEPARTMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:12.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）さすがに営業は\Nみんな 出払っちゃってるか
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.66,0:03:12.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone is away at meetings, of course...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:15.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:18.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いた！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:23.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）おはようございます\N（足音）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.16,0:03:26.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）どうも
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:26.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a message from Miss Tsubone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.83,0:03:29.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,坪根さんから 言づてがありました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.16,0:03:32.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,領収書を早めに出すように\Nとのことです
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.41,0:03:32.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Please ensure\Nyou submit the receipts ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.41,0:03:33.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それから…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:33.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.83,0:03:38.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,週末は いろいろ\Nご迷惑おかけしちゃったみたいで…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.00,0:03:39.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I was a pain at the weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:42.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,親切にしていただき\Nありがとうございました
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.20,0:03:41.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for helping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.00,0:03:44.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほんとに みっともない\Nところを―
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:45.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have been a sorry sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:45.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お見せしちゃって…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:47.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はっ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:55.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa. Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.29,0:03:53.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:54.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:55.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（結婚式の音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.91,0:03:55.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.66,0:03:56.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（結婚式の音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（結婚式の音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.12,0:03:57.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:58.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:03:57.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（結婚式の音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.37,0:03:58.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（結婚式の音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:03:59.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（結婚式の音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ～っ？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.66,0:04:01.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（結婚式の音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.83,0:04:02.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:03.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ～っ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.04,0:04:13.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）腰掛け！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.29,0:04:15.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Short-timer! Get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.08,0:04:16.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,これ 処理しとけ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.16,0:04:21.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,わああっ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:23.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ありがとうございます！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.29,0:04:25.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:25.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,精いっぱい頑張ります！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.58,0:04:28.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（トン）お… おう
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:28.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... right...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:30.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,腰掛け！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:31.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Short-timer! Tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:31.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,茶！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:39.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）は～い
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:39.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.54,0:04:45.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\N世界が いつもと違って見える
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.83,0:04:45.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world looks different.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.04,0:04:49.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,転職とか結婚退職とか―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.16,0:04:49.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Changing jobs,\Ngetting married and quitting...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,別に そんなこと\Nどうでもいいことだったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:52.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,That was never important!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.16,0:04:56.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,恋に生きれば よかったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.33,0:04:56.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,All I needed was love!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美(わしみ)･ゴリ）\N好きな人ができた！？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You've fallen for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,エヘヘ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.75,0:05:11.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）ん？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.33,0:05:13.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,これは…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.50,0:05:16.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She has completely fallen for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,だいぶ仕上がってるわね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,こないだまで “好きな人なんて\Nいない”って言ってたのに
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, she told us\Nthere was no one she liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.62,0:05:20.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）実戦経験がないだけで―
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She's inexperienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,実は結構 ほれっぽいタイプ\Nだったのかもしれないわね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.37,0:05:23.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems she's the type\Nthat falls in love easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:25.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）どんな人？\N（鷲美）写真ある？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.66,0:05:25.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-What is he like?\N-Do you have a photo?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:29.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but it's kind of embarrassing...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.62,0:05:30.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ありますけど～\N何か見せるの 恥ずかしいなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:33.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Show us!\N-Should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.20,0:05:33.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）見せなさいよ～\N（烈子）え～ どうしようかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:36.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）見せなさいよ～\N（烈子）どうしようかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Show us!\N-Should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.95,0:05:40.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）じゃ 見せなくていい\N（烈子）この人なんですけど～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.00,0:05:40.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-OK, then. It's no big deal.\N-Here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美･ゴリ）ああー…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:46.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）\Nか… かっこいいんじゃない？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.25,0:05:46.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems cool... I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.29,0:05:49.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ですよね かっこいいですよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.41,0:05:49.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? He's cool, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.41,0:05:51.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\N“あばたも えくぼ”って言うしね
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,They do say that love is blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:53.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）えっ？\N（鷲美）何でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.62,0:05:52.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-What?\N-Don't mind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.62,0:05:55.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,他に どんなとこがよかったの？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.75,0:05:55.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,What else do you like about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,え～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.50,0:05:58.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）教えてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:58.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.00,0:06:01.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,え～ どうしようかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.29,0:06:01.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, should I?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.62,0:06:02.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）じゃ 教えなくていい
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:03.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. It's no big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:06.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,When I got drunk, he helped me recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.08,0:06:07.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私が酔っ払ったとき\Nすっごく優しくしてくれたんですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.08,0:06:13.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,でも 優しいだけじゃなくて…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:12.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only is he kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,but, somehow,\Nthe air around him feels different.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.91,0:06:17.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何だか あの人の周りだけ\N空気が違ってて…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いつも どこか\N遠くを見てる感じで…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:20.37,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He's always staring into the distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:24.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,理由は よく分からないけど―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:23.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really know why...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.20,0:06:27.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,一緒にいると\N不思議と心が落ち着くんです
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:27.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,but when we're together, I feel calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,よかったわね 烈子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.29,0:06:32.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Retsuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:35.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）きっと すてきな人なのね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.70,0:06:35.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he's wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.62,0:06:38.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,アハハ… 恥ずかしいなあ
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.75,0:06:38.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This is embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:42.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あれ？ 何か思い出したら\N泣けてきちゃった 変なの
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:42.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting teary-eyed\Njust thinking about it. How strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go to the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.45,0:06:45.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ちょっと トイレ行ってきま～す
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:53.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ･鷲美）\Nかっこよくは ないわよね
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:52.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He is not cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.79,0:06:55.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）っていうか\Nこの人 あれに似てない？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:58.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy reminds me of\Na soft candy for babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.00,0:06:58.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ほら 赤ちゃんが食べる\N軟らかいお菓子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.75,0:07:02.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,分かる！ 私も同じこと思ってた
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:02.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? My thoughts exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,SALES DEPARTMENT
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:08.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸(まる)）何だよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.04,0:07:11.33,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Resasuke,\NI never realized you were so smooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.87,0:07:11.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,れさすけ お前\N意外と やるじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:14.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）えっ？ 何が？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:14.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:16.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,それだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,DID YOU FORGET YOUR INVOICE?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:20.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,SUBMIT YOUR RECEIPTS SOON - RETSUKO
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.45,0:07:24.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,〝烈子〞って こないだ\N合コンに来てた子だろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.62,0:07:24.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't Retsuko the girl\Nwho came to the mixer?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.54,0:07:27.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）うん とても\N仕事熱心な人みたいだね
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, she seems to be very diligent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:30.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Think again, idiot.\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.04,0:07:31.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸）はあ？\N違(ちげ)えよ バカ 何言ってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.37,0:07:36.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,どう見ても お前の気を引きたくて\Nわざわざ用事 作って 来てんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:35.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,She's obviously trying to nudge you\Ninto asking her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You can literally smell it in these notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:39.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,文面が醸し出す雰囲気で分かれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今度 デート誘ってやれ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.79,0:07:45.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask her out on a date.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:48.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）誰を？\N（マヌ丸）烈子ちゃんをだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.70,0:07:48.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Who?\N-Retsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.95,0:07:50.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）何で？\N（マヌ丸）“何で？”じゃねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.04,0:07:50.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Why?\N-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.95,0:07:52.29,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,俺が本当に お前を―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.04,0:07:55.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think I invited you\Nto the mixer just to even out the numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お飾りで 合コンに\N連れ出したと思ってんのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:59.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it because I'm worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.58,0:07:59.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,俺は これでも\Nお前を超心配してやってんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.62,0:08:01.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）何で？\N（マヌ丸）うああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.91,0:08:03.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Why?\N-You don't have a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.20,0:08:03.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,お前に彼女いねえからだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:05.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）でも…\N（マヌ丸）“でも”じゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-But...\N-Don't "but" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:08.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,いいか？ 今から お前に\N彼女を作るべき理由を―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:09.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I'll explain\Nwhy you need a girlfriend
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.50,0:08:09.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,論理的に分かりやすく―
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.83,0:08:13.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,段階を踏んで説明してやる\Nまず１つ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:11.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,in a simple and logical manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:12.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Reason one...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:21.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（目覚ましの音）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:29.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）今日も会えた
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.83,0:08:29.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, we meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.66,0:08:36.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,わあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.87,0:08:39.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.54,0:08:56.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,デートします？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.66,0:08:56.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to go on a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.37,0:08:58.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:58.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:10.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,TEA ROOM
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.37,0:09:13.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（携帯電話の操作音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.41,0:09:14.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S GO ON SUNDAY.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ウフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.62,0:09:23.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,WHERE AND WHEN SHOULD WE MEET?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:26.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（携帯電話の操作音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）10時に現地集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:29.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（携帯電話の操作音）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.50,0:09:30.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,10 a.m., at our destination...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）10時に現地集合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:34.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何で現地集合なんだよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.54,0:09:34.58,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't meet up at the destination!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.04,0:09:37.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,最寄り駅から\N一緒に行きゃあいいだろうが！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.16,0:09:37.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet her at the nearest station\Nand go together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Why?\N-Don't "why" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.58,0:09:39.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）何で？\N（マヌ丸）“何で？”じゃねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.45,0:09:42.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,LET'S MEET AT THE STATION.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.62,0:09:43.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ウフッ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.54,0:09:54.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I JUST ARRIVED.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.12,0:09:55.25,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,ARE YOU HERE?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.33,0:09:56.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,RESASUKE?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.70,0:09:59.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'M HERE.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:07.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ウフン
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.54,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（電車の走行音）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:16.20,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）今 私たち カップルです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:15.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, we're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:23.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how you look at it,\Nwe're a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.29,0:10:21.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,どっから どう見ても…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.37,0:10:23.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,カップルです
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:28.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,To everyone enjoying their day off,\Nexcuse my excitement.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.91,0:10:28.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,休日をお楽しみの皆さん\N大変お騒がせしております
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,今 私たちカップルが―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.20,0:10:32.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We, as a couple,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.08,0:10:36.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,テーマパークに入場いたしま～す
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.25,0:10:35.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,are about to visit an amusement park!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:46.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:52.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子の歌声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:52.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.70,0:10:57.00,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always crying inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:11:01.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけの歌声）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.37,0:11:01.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.16,0:11:06.70,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I was always daydreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:11.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Out-of-Pocket Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:16.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Metal Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.58,0:11:21.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子と\Nれさすけの歌声）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:23.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us met at a mixer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.29,0:11:31.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A drunken office mixer
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.66,0:11:42.29,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We work in different departments
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.83,0:11:48.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,But our hearts beat as one
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.70,0:11:49.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:12:00.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸）どうしてる？\Nちゃんとエスコートできてるか？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:12:02.66,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Did you escort her?\N-Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:02.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うん できてるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:06.79,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-Did you hold hands at sunset?\N-Yes, we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.75,0:12:05.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸）沈みゆく夕日を\N浴びながら 手をつないだか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:06.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,うん つないだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.75,0:12:08.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（マヌ丸）よーし 上出来だ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:08.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Great! Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:11.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,初デートってのは\N男が最初に値踏みされる場だからな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:11.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Men are judged on the first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.08,0:12:15.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,彼女に男らしいとこ 見せてやれよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.29,0:12:14.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Show her that you're a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.66,0:12:20.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,痛っ 痛たた… ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.79,0:12:19.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.87,0:12:23.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）ただいま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.04,0:12:26.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-I'm back.\N-Hello again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.04,0:12:26.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あっ おかえりなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.66,0:12:30.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あの…\Nずっと歩いてて疲れません？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect all this walking around\Nhas tired you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we find a restaurant\Nand take a break?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,どこか お店でも入って\N休みませんか？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.29,0:12:34.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.45,0:12:34.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.54,0:12:37.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）ん…\N（れさすけ）僕 全然疲れてないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.83,0:12:39.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not tired at all. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:39.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,行こう
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.62,0:12:41.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,はーい
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.66,0:12:41.50,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.95,0:12:56.62,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（花火の音）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:02.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（風の音）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.12,0:13:03.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）うう…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.87,0:13:05.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,あの…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.54,0:13:07.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,寒くないですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.25,0:13:10.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,大丈夫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.37,0:13:12.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine. I'm not cold at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,僕 全然寒くないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:15.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）んん…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.37,0:13:19.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.20,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAOKE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.20,0:13:20.16,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,は…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:21.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（くしゃみ）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,エヘヘ…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:26.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,もう すっごく楽しかったです！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.20,0:13:26.54,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,We had... so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:29.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）よかったじゃない！\N（鷲美）ムカついたりしなかった？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.95,0:13:29.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-That's great.\N-Was there anything you got upset about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.45,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,カップルで ああいう場所 行くと\Nけんかするって言うじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.08,0:13:32.75,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Couples usually fight\Nwhen they go to amusement parks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そんなこと 全然なかったですよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:35.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:38.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He took the lead\Nand made sure that I was enjoying myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:38.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私を楽しませようと\N積極的にリードしてくれて―
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:40.70,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,意外と頼れる人だなあって
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:40.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,He is surprisingly dependable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:43.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,痛っ 痛たたた…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:43.04,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:47.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\Nちょっと どうしたのよ？ その足
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.66,0:13:47.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, what happened to your foot?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.50,0:13:49.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（ゴリ）\Nだいぶ引っ張り回されたのね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:49.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he dragged her everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.41,0:13:52.95,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）\Nデートの相手って 男子中学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:53.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he a schoolboy or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.08,0:13:55.00,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,違いますよ～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.25,0:13:54.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,As it turns out, he's not very attentive.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.12,0:13:58.12,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）だとしたら\N随分 気遣いのない男ね
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.25,0:14:00.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私だったら 途中で帰るわよ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:02.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,-If I were you, I would have gone home.\N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.79,0:14:02.41,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.54,0:14:06.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,新しい靴なんか履いていった\N私が悪かったんです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.70,0:14:06.12,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,It was my fault\Nfor choosing brand new shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:13.62,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,SEND
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:16.25,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（デスメタルの音楽）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.37,0:14:17.50,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（鷲美）いつものやつ 歌ったら？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:19.95,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to sing your usual song?\NYou must have a lot of pent-up anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.79,0:14:19.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,何だかんだで\Nストレスたまったでしょ？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.04,0:14:22.83,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,そうよ！ 歌って\Nスッキリしちゃいなさい
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.37,0:14:22.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, release it by singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.66,0:14:31.58,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\N不満なんて 全然ないですから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.75,0:14:31.41,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing to complain about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.08,0:14:34.08,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,PAUSE
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:40.87,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,私 今 とっても幸せです
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:40.91,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really happy right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.45,0:14:44.04,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子）\N♪あなたは 自腹の
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.54,0:14:45.83,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Out-of-Pocket Prince
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.16,0:14:46.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪プリンス
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.20,0:14:48.08,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（れさすけ）\N♪君は メタルの
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:50.87,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the Metal Princess
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:50.75,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪プリンセス
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:53.33,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,（烈子･れさすけ）\N♪二人の出会いは
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:57.45,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us met at a mixer
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:57.79,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪合コン
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:00.66,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪飲みすぎた
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:05.16,Bot,,0000,0000,0000,,A drunken office mixer
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.79,0:15:06.37,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,♪社内合コン
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.50,0:15:10.91,Top,,0000,0000,0000,,～♪
